children.name: SELECT name FROM sqlite_master WHERE name <> 'sqlite_sequence' AND type IN ('table','view')

SELECT sql FROM
  (SELECT * FROM sqlite_master UNION ALL
   SELECT * FROM sqlite_temp_master)
WHERE type = 'table' AND name = 'relationships'

SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "users" INNER JOIN "relationships" ON "users"."id" = "relationships"."followed_id" WHERE "relationships"."follower_id" = ?

SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "microposts" WHERE (user_id IN (SELECT followed_id FROM relationships
                     WHERE  follower_id = 762146111)
                     OR user_id = 762146111)

SELECT "microposts".* FROM "microposts" WHERE (user_id IN (SELECT followed_id FROM relationships
                     WHERE  follower_id = 762146111)
                     OR user_id = 762146111) ORDER BY "microposts"."created_at" DESC LIMIT ? OFFSET ?
